task.summary: Changed ANSI coloring - now uses default background colour.
Updates to the guide and added support for TravisCI testing.
Added requirements.txt to .travis.yml for TravisCI testing.
Moved OS detection to function, added to sysinfo.
Minor fixes to comments in ssp.config.
Changed name of project (Simple Server Project).
Initial support for authentication; added ssp_auth_gen tool to generate login credentials for authentication support.
Updated guide with an authentication base64 encoding tool built-in (because why not?).
Fixed basic auth - it should work with all browsers now.
FreeBSD fixes (getOS didn't account for it).
Added *nix build script and added deps to index.html (and removed httpagentparser in favour of module from pypi).
